Navigate to the Add page using the nav bar at the top of the web page, this allows to add new books to the database,
after entering the details press the button at the bottom of the page to add a new boook.

Once a new book is added then navigate to the display page, this allows to view the added book.

Under each new added book there are two buttons one to delete the entry from the database another to chage it.

If the delete button is pressed the database will be updated and that information deleted out of it.

If the change button is pressed, a change page pops up and allows the user to change the information in the database,
once this information is updated, the useer should then  press the button at the bottom of the age to update the databse,
to see the results the user can then navigate back to the display page.
